Lecture :1
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Shotcuts
------------
Command + option + J        -> Developer Mode in Chrome
Cmd+Option+U                -> source Code
CMD + Shift + P             -> Format Document
Shift + Option + A          -> Multiline Commments 
Command + /                 -> Single Line Comment




Formatter
------------
Add Extension "Prettier - Code formatter"
Add Extension "Bracket Pair Colorization Toggler"




Install Node
-------------
node -v
brew install node
npm -v




Configure Project Using npm
-----------------------------
npm init -y
Or
npm init

npm install -D parcel     (for Dev dependency)
npm install parcel     (for normal dependency)




Lecture : 2
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ignite the app
-----------------
npx parcel index.html         (For developer build)
npx parcel build index.html   (for prod build)




install React
-----------------
installing react throught the CDN link [https://legacy.reactjs.org/docs/cdn-links.html] is not preferrable (as we did in index5.html)

npm install react
npm i react-dom

broswerList
[https://browserslist.dev/?q=bGFzdCAyIHZlcnNpb25z]





Lecture : 3
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// To run the scripts present in the package.json <script>
npm run start
or
npm start

npm run build

-> Functional Component



